  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Safety &amp; Efficacy of Subcutaneous Methylnaltrexone on Opioid-Induced Constipation in Cancer Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Trial Evaluating the Safety and Efficacy of Subcutaneous Methylnaltrexone for the Treatment of Opioid-Induced Constipation in Subjects With Cancer-Related Pain</official_title>
